channel.title: MTP - Multi World Server
channel.description:
Ok so far so good. I am using pk planet base and and F2P server base. World 1 is pk planet base and world 2 is this F2p pking base. I plan to add atleast 5 more worlds by the end of the weekend.
If this isnt aloud mod please remove this sentence but if you wish to test out the server please pm me about it.
I will be posting progress for this as it goes on.
4/23/10 - 2 worlds being hosted 24/7. few bugs fixed in both servers
